IFPREVERB KILL -1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 1
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 294
  IFVAR INTNUM3 ! 304
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Granite's icy glare bores into your skull. He grabs you and throws you out headfirst,
  ECHO PLAYER you barely catch the ladder before plummeting to your death. You hear him cursing you
  ECHO PLAYER from within the bar.
  ECHO OTHERS Granite grabs %n by the collar and pants and heaves him out over the cliff. "Try
  ECHO OTHERS that agin and I won't be sa nice to yer!" He walks back behind the bar swearing
  ECHO OTHERS obscure deeplander curses.
  MOVE 621
  POSITION LAY
  ENDIF
  ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF

