NUMBER 3714
NAME Hallway
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL

CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
A typical hallway. A stairway leads down into a cavernous room. There are
two doors here, one made of oak, the other made of rosewood. A large painting
of Mad and Demetrius rests on the far wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 1 1226 VAL2=3715
ITEM 2 943 ADJ1=366 VAL1=300 VAL2=3716 VAL3=3716 CLOSED LOCKED
ITEM 3 943 ADJ1=216 VAL1=300 VAL2=3717 VAL3=3717 CLOSED LOCKED
ITEM 4 345 ADJ1=178
EXTEND 4 of Mad and Demetrius
ITEM 5 379

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 4
You see before you a large painting of Mad and Demetrius standing in front of what
looks like a cave. A rather interesting sign hangs above them. "Hammer and Anvil"
is the only caption.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM BEHIND 4
You walk up close to wall, and place your head against it to look behind it. You
see there is a gap, and something imbedded in the wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END

VARIABLE MADDEMSAFE
VARIABLE MADSAFECOMBO
VARIABLE MADR1
VARIABLE MADR2
VARIABLE MADL1
VARIABLE TEMPPVAL55
VARIABLE TEMPCOUNTMONEY

IFPREVERB PULL 4
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER The painting has already been pulled open on it's hinges.
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO OTHERS %N gives a good tug on the right-hand edge of the painting, and it swings away from the wall.
    ECHO PLAYER You give a good tug on the right-hand edge of the painting, and it swings away from the wall.
    EQUAL MADDEMSAFE 1
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PUSH 4
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You give the painting a hearty push and it swings back towards the wall
    ECHO PLAYER on its hinges. A moment later you hear a "click" as it catches the latch.
    ECHO OTHERS %n gives the painting a hearty push and it swings back towards the wall
    ECHO OTHERS on its hinges. A moment later you hear a "click" as it catches the latch.
	EQUAL MADDEMSAFE 0
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You push against the painting and it remains firmly attached to the wall.
  ENDIF
ENDIF


IFPREVERB FLIP 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 1
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You give the knob a good spin in both directions, resetting it.
    ECHO OTHERS %n spins the knob several times in each direction.
    EQUAL MADR1 0
    EQUAL MADL1 0
    EQUAL MADR2 0
    EQUAL MADSAFECOMBO 1
  ENDIF
ENDIF


IFPREVERB LOOK 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 0
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER What are you referring to?  Please be more specific.
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER You see a small knob with many numbers etched around it. It seems to be imbedded into the wall.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB READ 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 0
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER What are you referring to?  Please be more specific.
  ELSE
    CLEARVERB
    STRCVT 0 MADSAFECOMBO
    ECHO PLAYER You see that the knob reads %0.
  ENDIF
ENDIF

IFPREVERB PUSH 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 1
    CLEARVERB

    SUB MADSAFECOMBO 1
    IFVAR MADSAFECOMBO = 0
      EQUAL MADSAFECOMBO 15
    ENDIF
    STRCVT 0 MADSAFECOMBO
    ECHO PLAYER You turn the knob one position to the left. It now reads %0.
    ECHO OTHERS %n turns the knob.
    IFVAR MADSAFECOMBO = 2
      IFVAR MADR1 = 1
        EQUAL MADL1 1
      ELSE
        EQUAL MADL1 0
      ENDIF
    ENDIF

  ENDIF


    IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
      STRCVT 2 MADR1
      STRCVT 3 MADL1
      STRCVT 4 MADR2
      ECHO PLAYER MADR1=%2  MADL1=%3 MADR2=%4
    ENDIF

ENDIF


IFPREVERB TURN 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 1
    CLEARVERB

    ADD MADSAFECOMBO 1

    IFVAR MADSAFECOMBO = 16
      EQUAL MADSAFECOMBO 1
    ENDIF

    STRCVT 0 MADSAFECOMBO
    ECHO PLAYER You turn the knob one position to the right. It now reads %0.
    ECHO OTHERS %n turns the knob.

    IFVAR MADSAFECOMBO = 9
      IFVAR MADR1 = 0
        EQUAL MADR1 1
      ELSE
        IFVAR MADL1 = 0
          EQUAL MADR1 0
          EQUAL MADL1 0
        ENDIF
      ENDIF
    ENDIF

    IFVAR MADSAFECOMBO = 10
      IFVAR MADL1 = 1
        IFVAR MADR1 = 1

  EQUAL MADR1 0
          EQUAL MADL1 0

  IFVAR PVAL55 > 0

  ADD PVAL50 PVAL55
          EQUAL TEMPPVAL55 PVAL55
          MULT TEMPPVAL55 3
          DIV TEMPPVAL55 4
          STRCVT 1 TEMPPVAL55
          GMMSG ** %N gets %1 gold coins from Demetrius and Mad's safe.
          NEWITEM 8 161 ADJ3=147
          SETITEMVAL 8 1 TEMPPVAL55
          EQUAL TEMPPVAL55 0
          EQUAL PVAL55 0
          ECHO PLAYER With an audible "click" the knob swings open to reveal the inside
          ECHO PLAYER of a small safe. As you finish opening the safe, you see %1 gold
          ECHO PLAYER coins spill out onto the floor.
          ECHO OTHERS The knob makes an audible "click" and then opens.
          ECHO PLAYER %cYou then swing the knob closed.
          ECHO OTHERS %c%N swings the knob closed.

  ELSE

  ECHO PLAYER With an audible "click" the knob swings open to reveal the inside
          ECHO PLAYER of a small safe. It appears to be empty. You swing it closed.
          ECHO OTHERS %c%N swings the knob closed.

  ENDIF

        ENDIF
      ELSE
      	IFVAR MADR1 = 1
      	  EQUAL MADR1 0
      	ENDIF
      ENDIF
    ENDIF

    IFVAR INTNUM3 = 1
      STRCVT 2 MADR1
      STRCVT 3 MADL1
      STRCVT 4 MADR2
      ECHO PLAYER MADR1=%2  MADL1=%3 MADR2=%4
    ENDIF

  ENDIF
ENDIF


IFTOUCH 5
  IFVAR MADDEMSAFE = 0
    CLEARVERB
    ECHO PLAYER What are you referring to?  Please be more specific.
  ENDIF
ENDIF


NUMBER 3716
NAME Demetrius and Tyaa's Room
INDOOR_FLOOR
FIXED_LIGHT
ASTRAL

CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room holds two beds, one large bed in one corner of the room, and
across the room, a smaller bed, which is child size. The smaller bed is
red with pictures of beautiful wolves running across it. The larger bed
has a fluffy pillow on it shaped like a wolf, and a black blanket with
stars covering it. The rest of the room is carved smoothly into the
wall, and on some of the slick walls are pictures. Many toys of all
sorts seem to be cluttered under the smaller bed, hidden away from the
rest of the room. A glass case filled with water rests on a table.
Swimming freely in the cage, among many rocks and plants, are all
different kinds of fish, all different colors.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 1 85  ; small bed
ITEM 2 355  ; large bed
ITEM 3 91  ; table
ITEM 4 944 ADJ1=366 VAL2=3714 CLOSED UNLATCHED
ITEM 5 1308 ADJ1=502 ADJ2=52
ITEM 6 1308

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 5
The two blobs resolve themselves into a larger blob, wearing a magician's
hat, and a smaller blob with long red hair. The portrait is lettered with
'mIstr DeMtruS n tYaa' and is signed, in huge clumsy letters, 'TYAA'.
*DESCRIPTION_END

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
You see a dark and winterey scene set in a snow-laddened pine forest. A
pack of wolves are locked in fierce combat with a lone, erect werewolf,
whose eye's glow red with fire.
*DESCRIPTION_END

NUMBER 3717
NAME Mad's Room
FIXED_LIGHT
INDOOR_FLOOR
ASTRAL

CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
This room is perfectly square shaped and carved out like the rest of
the bar. A pile of leaves sits in the corner of the room; two pillows
are partially burried within. The only other adornments are two
paintings and six cushions used for seats.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 1 345 ; painting1

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
This painting is a pecular sight. It depicts a mountainous background
with a forest of pines in the foreground. Jutting from the left hand
edge is a long wodden stick with five metal strings running the length of
it. They are tied at the end with metal knobs. A hand, fingers
actually, is depressing some of the strings. A lone peace dove sits
on the stick. It is wearing sunglasses.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 2 345 ; painting2

*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
A man sits on the floor of a darkened room, his arms wrapped around
his folded knees. His head is beant back and he is howling in
despair. Behind him tank hold peculiar fish. A green recliner is the
only decoration. The title at the bottem simply read "After Quest
Tech". The painting leaves you slightly disturbed.
*DESCRIPTION_END

