*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
Tacked to the stone wall, the vibrant colors woven into the
mosaic display a battle of improbable odds. A black- robed
figure and a 7ft tall wolfling are engaged in combat against the
denizens of the Deep Forest. Lupo shamen employ the arcane arts,
while a pack of greater werewolves, and several wolverines bring
physical force to the fray. As the black-robed figure points to
the sky, eldritch light streaks from his gauntlets towards the
heavens. A moment later, meteors crash among the wolf host. An
orange glow about the wolfling turns to dust the plant snares
reaching for him. You catch a hint of emerald green as the wolf
lord wields his black- grey staff. Considering the existence of
the mosaic, you surmise that perhaps the odds werent so poor
after all.
*DESCRIPTION_END

