      ECHO PLAYER You are pushed back by an incredibly powerful magical force!
      ECHO OTHERS %n is pushed back by an incredibly powerful magical force!
    ELSE
       IFVAR PLRSINROOM > 1
         VARIABLE JASSECURE
         EQUAL JASSECURE PLRSINROOM
         SUB JASSECURE 1
         STRCVT 0 JASSECURE
         IFVAR JASSECURE = 1
           STRCVT 0 JASSECURE
           ECHO PLAYER %cA magical voice whispers to you, "There are %0 person here with you."
           SPELL 406 100
         ELSE
          STRCVT 0 JASSECURE
           ECHO PLAYER %cA magical voice whispers to you, "There are %0 people here with you."
           SPELL 406 100
           SPELL 406 100
           SPELL 406 100
           SPELL 406 100
         ENDIF
       ENDIF
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF

