NUMBER 471
NAME Garden
FOREST
DAY_LIGHT
ASTRAL

CALL 33
ITEM 9 693
*DESCRIPTION_START
As you gaze around the garden, a riotous mix of colors assaults your eyes.
Taylor and Garin have brought back cuttings and clippings from their
journeys, and have raised a garden unrivalled in Fayd. Trees that were
thought to grow only in somewhat chillier climes, such as an uquart, grow
here thanks to Taylor's skill in magic. Tropical ferns and shrubs grow
here as well; you recognize plants that have been transplanted from islands
to the south of here. The garden extends a small way towards the sea;
there is a path that wanders down to the shore from here.
*DESCRIPTION_END

ITEM 1 80 VAL2=534
ITEM 2 943 ADJ1=355 VAL1=280 VAL2=469 VAL3=469 CLOSED LOCKED

IFVERB SMELL -1
  ECHO PLAYER %cYou wander through the garden, gazing with delight at the variety of blooms here. As you breath deeply, the perfume of the flowers tickles your nose.
ENDIF

IFVERB LISTEN -1
  ECHO PLAYER %cIt would appear that along with the flora, some native fauna has made itself at home here. You hear the rustling amongst the higher branches, and the occasional call of a songbird.
ENDIF

